{"tid":2149462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西灣河開槍警申司法覆核　指私人檢控涉違憲","createTime":"2020-08-10T12:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T12:33:39.000Z","uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61dfee454d81a4837f7a7b3e7e1e5dd081e0e6da","tid":2149462,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%AD%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E6%8F%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E6%B2%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6%E7%94%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E6%8C%87%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=2ce5e430\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2%2F&h=0e242056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%AD%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E6%8F%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E6%B2%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6%E7%94%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E6%8C%87%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2/</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員許智峯，早前就一名警員去年 11 月 11 日開槍事件提出私人檢控，獲裁判官林子勤受理，並排期 8 月 31 日開庭處理。涉案警員今（10 日）入稟高等法院申請司法覆核，要求法庭推翻裁判官相關決定，並宣告普通法下的私人檢控違反《基本法》第 63 條，條文列明律政司主管刑事檢察工作；以及申請臨時禁制令擱置私人檢控程序，直至是次司法覆核有結果為止。申請人於入稟狀中指，許智峯申請私人檢控的動機不良，是意圖羞辱警隊及煽動他人對警隊的憎恨等。"},{"pid":"9a9118a27fe5e3c79cf1e3147c9c6f5d3e48e15f","tid":2149462,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2187435c78f035e632eb0714fcc2c4b5be361db","tid":2149462,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"【有圖】點解呢個靚仔咁後生就要揸柺杖？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2141275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2141275</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b13ab8e0fd5330174e78544b16b1d18a3e9b7ea3","tid":2149462,"uid":55597,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:14:41.000Z","msg":"私人檢控違反基本法？<br />\n咁即係香港政府犯法容許私人檢控？"},{"pid":"104ff5f6e16cbc96fea0224f7c1c69d433ef2543","tid":2149462,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"等睇許智峯比人用國安法拉"},{"pid":"780cff9278cd719656044f7990acd6c5e479cdb6","tid":2149462,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"104ff5f6e16cbc96fea0224f7c1c69d433ef2543","tid":2149462,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"等睇許智峯比人用國安法拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:21:36.000Z","msg":"過幾日就去搞佢架啦應該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e9b5d01476152ec53230d8a4cf8e9a57aa57fc","tid":2149462,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\